.\" playfield.1.mdoc - Playfield manpage
.Dd September 2025
.Dt PLAYFIELD 1
.Os Playfield 1.0
.Sh NAME
.Nm playfield
.Nd lightweight 2D game engine and script runtime
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
is a lightweight, cross-platform 2D game engine and scripting runtime
based on the NoctLang virtual machine.
It provides fast JIT compilation on desktop platforms and a
high-performance interpreter on others.
.Pp
When invoked,
.Nm
automatically executes the script
.Pa main.pf
from the current working directory.
No other script files can be specified on the command line.
.Sh EXAMPLES
Run the engine in a project directory containing
.Pa main.pf :
.Bd -literal -offset indent
cd mygame/
playfield
.Ed
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr playfield-compiler 1 ,
.Xr playfield-pack 1
